description:
Dive into the profound mystery of the investigative judgment as foretold in Daniel 7:9-11, where every person's choices and desires are scrutinized before Jesus' second coming. This pivotal moment ensures that no one faces a destiny unaligned with their true intentions. Discover how this divine process underscores God's justice and His non-coercive nature, inviting us to choose our path freely. Explore the significance of each decision we make and how it determines our place in God's eternal kingdom. Join us as we unravel the mysteries of faith, choice, and divine judgment in this enlightening exploration.

To watch the full video from Elder Ted Wilson, president of the General Conference of Seventh-day Adventists, paste this link into your browser:
https://youtu.be/7tjx7o9d_ms
